assetProfile.longBusinessSummary: Technical Publications Service S.p.A. provides technical, engineering, and communication services in Italy. The company provides aviation mission equipment including turnkey solutions, such as medical, aerial work, avionic, and customization kit; and design and cost engineering, which design and develops components, devices, and systems, as well as engages in analysis and simulations, cost engineering and benchmarking, and gear boxes services. It also offers technical publishing and training comprising logistics, process and standards, and technical regulations, training, and services; and information technologies and avionic services, which includes software development and testing, test program set, avionics systems integration, and application design and development services. In addition, the company provides digital content management, such as communication and marketing, and augmented and virtual reality. It serves aeronautics and space, defence, automotive, truck and buses, special vehicles, oil and gas, railways, and ropeways and garaging system sectors. The company was founded in 1964 and is headquartered in Gallarate, Italy. Technical Publications Service S.p.A. is a subsidiary of G&D S.R.L.
